Class SwitchNode

    public class SwitchNode
extends AbstractNode
implements InlineNode
    List of conditional cases {code} if (a) { ... someStatements if a == true.. } else if (b) { ... someStatements if b == true.. } else { ... someStatements in other cases ... }
